<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>As I’ve not heard back from any of my previous attempts to move forward with your business insurance, I will now be closing your quote on our system.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>However, if you are</span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;interested in proceeding with a policy</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;at any time in the future, please reply to let me know the best date and time for me to call you to set up a new quote.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="Aptos, sans-serif">Alternatively, you can always give me a ring on&nbsp;</font></span><b style="font-family: Aptos, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-family: Aptos, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Kind regards</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white;">,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
